# HTML Site Standards

## Design
- Use Inter or Plus Jakarta Sans from Google Fonts
- Default accent: `#6366f1` — swap to brand color if provided
- Minimum font size: 16px body, 14px captions
- Buttons: rounded (`border-radius: 8px`), clear hover states

## Sections (landing pages)
Always include in this order: nav → hero → features/services → about → CTA → footer

## Performance
- No jQuery or heavy libraries
- Lazy-load images with `loading="lazy"`
- Minify only on final export

## Accessibility
- All images need `alt` text
- Use `<button>` for actions, `<a>` for navigation
- Color contrast ratio minimum 4.5:1
